title: EastEnders star Danny Dyer’s mum reveals her fears over star’s boozy antics and admits she begged Alan Carr not to get actor drunk
text:
TV Magazine 'YOU HAVE BEEN WARNED' EastEnders star Danny Dyer’s mum reveals her fears over star’s boozy antics and admits she begged Alan Carr not to get actor drunk 
Actor tried to give up drinking last month, but cracked and went on a series of benders and angered BBC bosses Exclusive
